---
---
<section id="imagine" class="relative bg-paper text-ink py-12 sm:py-14 md:py-16 lg:py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-32 -right-16 w-[280px] h-[280px] sm:w-[400px] sm:h-[400px] md:w-[560px] md:h-[560px] rounded-full bg-gold/10 blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-32 -left-16 w-[240px] h-[240px] sm:w-[340px] sm:h-[340px] md:w-[480px] md:h-[480px] rounded-full bg-midnight/5 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 md:px-10 relative">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 md:gap-14 lg:gap-20 items-center">

      <!-- Image column — poetic mood shot -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 order-2 md:order-1">
        <figure class="relative w-full aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl shadow-2xl bg-midnight">
          <img
            src="/images/marina.jpeg"
            alt="A sailing yacht mast reflected in still marina water at sunrise"
            loading="lazy"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-[30%] bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <figcaption class="absolute bottom-5 left-5 md:bottom-6 md:left-6 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-eyebrow2 text-paper/70">
            <span class="inline-block w-4 h-px bg-gold mr-2 align-middle"></span>
            The view is the occasion
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 order-1 md:order-2">
        <p class="eyebrow">Close your eyes</p>
        <h2 class="display text-fluid-h1 mt-5 sm:mt-6">
          Imagine a morning<br/>
          that begins on the water<br/>
          <span class="text-ink/45 italic">and ends inside a memory<br/>your children will keep forever.</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 space-y-5 sm:space-y-6 text-fluid-lead leading-relaxed font-light text-ink/80 max-w-prose">
          <p>
            Imagine the sound of a canal, unhurried, moving past your window.
            The soft glow of lanterns on a promenade you haven&rsquo;t walked yet.
            A skyline of storybook silhouettes just beyond the palm line.
          </p>
          <p>
            Imagine a garden that comes alive at dusk. A boardwalk that leads
            to the tide. A restaurant lit like a small planet, waiting for you.
          </p>
          <p class="text-midnight font-normal">
            This isn&rsquo;t a resort. Isn&rsquo;t a getaway. It&rsquo;s the address you come home to.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
